t;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;感谢小黄提供的照片&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:10px 0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n											&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;border:2px dashed #C0C8D1;width:532px;display:inline-block;background-color:#EFEFEF;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;出租车司机小黄，勤劳、朴实，以前疼老婆是出了名的，可后来发展到了“怕老婆”，原因就是正值壮年，平时经常感觉腰背酸痛，干什么都提不起劲儿来；尿频明显，最让他痛心的是：经常到了关键时刻小弟弟却不争气，好不容易“雄起”了，小弟弟还心不甘情不愿，力不从心。&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;最尴尬&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;的是还没有进入，就结束了。老婆却出奇平静的背过身去说：累一天了，早点睡吧。这八个字就象利剑一样刺入了身体，让他痛彻心扉！为了这，小黄还自己吃了很多产品，可是吃的时间长了效果也不明显了。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;-----------------------------------&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#EC1C07;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#EC1C07;&quot;&gt;两个月前&lt;/span&gt;，小黄也是他的一个熟人带到我这里来的，开始按照我的产品调理。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#EC1C07;&quot;&gt;服用当天&lt;/span&gt;，疲劳乏力、腰酸腿软、出虚汗就得到缓解；&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#EC1C07;&quot;&gt;三天后&lt;/span&gt;，头晕、易烦躁、尿频、尿急的症状就明显改善，有了明显的冲动。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#EC1C07;&quot;&gt;一周后&lt;/span&gt;，小弟弟每天精神抖擞，雄起速度快，意念到，小弟到，收发自如，罢工和快枪手的情况再也没有发生；时间能控制在30分钟左右。老婆开玩笑说用了这个产品像换了个人似的。到现在已经坚持了两个多月了，时间可随意控制，再也不像以前事后出汗倒头就睡觉了，现在还可以和老婆说说话。小黄很自信的说，“&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;现在要补偿这几年对老婆的亏欠，只怕老婆吃不消&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;”。&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;\r\n										&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n											&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#D92142;font-size:20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n微信号：&lt;span class=&quot;rand_wxh&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 2px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFF00;&quot;&gt;Lzyys123&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;（复制添加）&lt;/span&gt;\r\n										&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100