:532px;display:inline-block;background-color:#EFEFEF;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 小廖也同样是一位深受其害的朋友，刚三十出头，就“不行了”，平时经常感觉腰背酸痛，神疲乏力，失眠，多梦，干什么都提不起劲儿来；头晕耳鸣，最让他痛心的是：两三月才勉强过一次性生活，还中途疲软，事后大量出虚汗，每次都让老婆饥渴难忍！老婆总说他“无能、不是个男人”，这让小廖的自尊心饱受摧残。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF0000;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;一个月前，小廖开始按照李俊老先生的办法进行调理。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;现在已经坚持了一个月了，用小廖自己的话讲：真是重新找回了做男人的感觉，夫妻生活和谐。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:10px 0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;border:2px dashed #C0C8D1;width:532px;display:inline-block;background-color:#EFEFEF;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;别小看这产品，&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;城里面一些老板开着车子常来我这里要产品，&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;小廖当时过来的时候是尿次尿量较多，未重视，二年前发现头晕加重，腰酸，心悸面色苍白，结果是气血亏损严重。&lt;/strong&gt;后服用二月后，&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;感觉舒服多了&lt;/span&gt;。也有些男性问题的朋友过来。试了以后感觉都很不错!&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0.5em 0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-s