mp;nbsp;\r\n					&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/20170308/3b8343065df94e1f441cf1acca4bf46a.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;（李俊孙子图）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;color:#FF8124;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;李俊老先生的孙子，就是严重的肾气亏，功能&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;障碍，各种补品，虽然用过不少，但是收效甚微。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:10px 0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;border:16px solid #FF8124;-webkit-border-image:none 50 fill;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n						&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/20170308/e6fbcf6f5b3c4911ded9615da0c99508.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt; \r\n					&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n						&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:25.6px;text-indent:2em;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;一般男人年过三十，身体就开始走下坡路，平衡被打破，出现肾虚。若长期抽烟、喝酒、熬夜等不良的生活习惯，身体问题更会加重。最明显的感觉 是：每天感觉很累，疲劳乏力、腰酸背痛、头晕眼花、出虚汗、膀胱的“水龙头”拧不紧、憋不住尿、尿频、尿急、夫妻生活更是力不从心、疲软无力。我制作这个 产品，最开始，其实就是为了治我孙子的肾虚肾亏，没想到效果十分理想，这才想到公开此产品，让那些和他一样饱受：气血亏损，时间短等问题的朋友，都能从中 受益。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n					&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF0000;font-size:21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 我孙女是湖北知名大学毕业的，她研究院的有几位老师也都在用我的产品。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0.5em 0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:532px;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/20170308/c41f8272c023f4f0d21fabf6ce380d07.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;484&quot; height=&quot;680&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-source=&quot;bj.96weixin.com&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;clear:both;min-height:1em;&quot;&gt;\r\n					